# ExpenseCategory

Criar categoria:
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/expense_categories \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"name": "Transporte"}'
~~~

Listar todas as categorias:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expense_categories
~~~

Obter categoria por ID:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expense_categories/1
~~~

Atualizar categoria:
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/expense_categories/1 \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"name": "Alimentação"}'
~~~

Deletar categoria:
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expense_categories/1
~~~

# User

Criar um user:
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/users \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "João Silva",
    "email": "joao@example.com",
    "mobileNumber": 912345678,
    "birthdate": "1990-01-01",
    "passwordHash": "hashed_password",
    "lastLogin": "2024-04-10",
    "amountSaved": 123.45
  }'
~~~

Listar todos os users:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
~~~

Obter um user por ID:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
~~~

Atualizar um user:
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "João Atualizado",
    "email": "joao.novo@example.com",
    "mobileNumber": 911223344,
    "birthdate": "1990-01-01",
    "passwordHash": "new_hashed_password",
    "lastLogin": "2025-04-10",
    "amountSaved": 200.00
  }'
~~~

Deletar um user:
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
~~~

# ExpenseLabel

Criar um expense_label:
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/expense-labels \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "userId": 1,
    "categoryId": 1,
    "name": "Gasolina",
    "target": 150.00,
    "spent": 60.25
  }'

~~~

Listar todos os expense_labels:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expense-labels
~~~

Obter um expense_label por ID:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expense-labels/1
~~~

Atualizar um expense_label:
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/expense-labels/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "userId": 1,
    "categoryId": 1,
    "name": "Gasolina Atualizada",
    "target": 200.00,
    "spent": 80.50
  }'
~~~

Deletar um expense_label:
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expense-labels/1
~~~

# Expense

POST criar nova expense:
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "labelId": 1,
    "userId": 1,
    "value": 25.50,
    "occurrenceDate": "2025-04-09",
    "insertionDate": "2025-04-10"
  }'
~~~

GET todas as expenses:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
~~~

GET uma expense por ID:
~~~
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1
~~~


PUT atualizar uma expense existente:
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "labelId": 1,
    "userId": 1,
    "value": 30.75,
    "occurrenceDate": "2025-04-09",
    "insertionDate": "2025-04-10"
  }'
~~~

DELETE uma expense:
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1
~~~

# FixedExpense

Criar uma fixed_expense (POST):
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/fixed_expenses \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "userId": 1,
    "labelId": 1,
    "value": 150.75,
    "startDate": "2024-04-01",
    "frequency": "01:00:00",
    "insertionDate": "2024-04-10"
  }'
~~~

Listar todas as fixed_expenses (GET):
~~~
curl http://localhost:8080/api/fixed_expenses
~~~

Obter uma fixed_expense específica por ID (GET):
~~~
curl http://localhost:8080/api/fixed_expenses/1
~~~

Atualizar uma fixed_expense (PUT):
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/fixed_expenses/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "userId": 1,
    "labelId": 1,
    "value": 200.00,
    "startDate": "2024-04-01",
    "frequency": "00:30:00",
    "insertionDate": "2024-04-10"
  }'
~~~

Apagar uma fixed_expense (DELETE):
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/fixed_expenses/1
~~~

# ExpenseTarget

Criar um novo Expense Target:
~~~
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/expense_targets \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "expenseCategoryId": 1,
    "userId": 1,
    "target": 500
  }'
~~~

Buscar todos os Expense Targets:
~~~
curl http://localhost:8080/api/expense_targets
~~~

Buscar um Expense Target específico:
~~~
curl http://localhost:8080/api/expense_targets/1/1
~~~

Atualizar um Expense Target:
~~~
curl -X PUT http://localhost:8080/api/expense_targets/1/1 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "expenseCategoryId": 1,
    "userId": 1,
    "target": 750
  }'
~~~

Apagar um Expense Target:
~~~
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expense_targets/1/1
~~~

